'''耶范特·特奇安'''（{{lang-en|Yervant Terzian}}，{{bd|1939年|2月9日|2019年|11月25日|catIdx=Terzian}}）是一位[[美国|美国]][[天文学|天文学]]家，1979至1999年间为[[康奈尔大学|康奈尔大学]]天文学院教授
<ref name="CornellObi">{{cite news |last1=Friedlander |first1=Blaine |title=Yervant Terzian, who explored matter between stars, dies at 80 |url=http://news.cornell.edu/stories/2019/12/yervant-terzian-who-explored-matter-between-stars-dies-80 |work=[[Cornell_Chronicle|Cornell Chronicle]] |publisher=Cornell University |date=December 4, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208151501/http://news.cornell.edu/stories/2019/12/yervant-terzian-who-explored-matter-between-stars-dies-80 |archivedate=8 December 2019}}</ref>
，主要著作有《卡尔·萨根的宇宙》（''Carl Sagan's Universe''）等，曾为《[[天文物理期刊|天文物理期刊]]》（''	The Astrophysical Journal''）的编辑<ref name="CornellBio">{{cite web |title=Yervant Terzian |url=https://astro.cornell.edu/yervant-terzian |publisher=[[Cornell_University|Cornell University]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208151047/https://astro.cornell.edu/yervant-terzian |archivedate=8 December 2019}}</ref>

==生平==
耶范特·特奇安1939年出生在[[埃及王國|埃及王國]]的[[亚历山大港|亚历山大港]]，母亲是[[希腊人|希腊]]渔家女，父亲是[[亚美尼亚人|亚美尼亚]]商人，且是[[亚美尼亚种族灭绝|亚美尼亚大屠杀]]的幸存者<ref name="funeralhome"/><ref name="ArAS_bio">{{cite web |title=Yervant TERZIAN (b. 1939) |url=https://www.aras.am/FamousAstronomers/terzian.html |website=aras.am |publisher=Armenian Astronomical Society |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026122048/http://www.aras.am/FamousAstronomers/terzian.html |archivedate=26 October 2016}}</ref><ref name="CornellObi"/>。他在开罗的亚美尼亚学校完成了初等教育，之后进入[[開羅美國大學|開羅美國大學]]就读本科，1960年毕业后移民美国，在[[印第安纳大学|印第安纳大学]]就读，分别于1963年和1965年获得天文学的硕士与博士学位<ref name="funeralhome">{{cite news |title=Dr. Yervant Terzian, PhD. |url=https://www.bangsfuneralhome.com/obituary/dr-yervant-terzian-phd |work=bangsfuneralhome.com |agency=Bangs Funeral Home, Inc. |date=December 6, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208151747/https://www.bangsfuneralhome.com/obituary/dr-yervant-terzian-phd |archivedate=8 December 2019 }}. Also published in {{cite web |title=Dr. Yervant Terzian, PhD. |url=https://www.legacy.com/obituaries/name/dr-yervant-terzian-phd-obituary?pid=194542558 |website=legacy.com |publisher=[[legacy.com|legacy.com]] |accessdate=9 December 2019 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209092639/https://www.legacy.com/obituaries/name/dr-yervant-terzian-phd-obituary?pid=194542558 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CornellObi"/>。

